> There was a nod from DINOBOT as VICE GRIP was dumped into the CR Chamber.
> "Yes.  Of the things that never changed were that the spider could be always
> trusted to have his own agenda going on."
>
> Pausing, and then internally playing back, "There was a different level of
> reverb in his internal communication.  There was a slight echo to it that
> was not within his normal vocalizer tone.  Someone else was in the room wtih
> him."
>
> Glancing at SKY SHADOW as the two walked along, "Can you ask the computer to
> tell us then who is with him at the moment?"

<NEW>

TARANTULUS' voice came over the radio to HYDRAS, "I have just
ressurected another soldier down here." There was another cackle from
TARANTULUS. "She is ready for visitors now." He said with a touch of
humor.

SKY SHADOW looked annoyed briefly and then nodded and smiled as he
considered DINOBOT's suggestion. "Computer." he said speaking outloud,
obviously wanting HYDRAS and the rest to hear the results. "How many
individuals are with unit TARANTULUS?" he said with authority.

"Proccessing." The computer came back. "There is one other individual
with Predacon unit Tarantulus. Predacon unit Blackarachnia."

"Oh?" SKY SHADOW said with a curious look on his face. "This might be
interesting after all."

FRACTYL looked at SKY SHADOW and then HYDRAS, "What's she doing here,
and isn't she a Maximal?" There was a confused look on his face to say
thr least.

CRYOTEK nodded, "It would seem that I am not the only one bearing
gifts." he said with a slightly disappointed note in his voice. "But
then again there are more projects in the works." He said cryptically.

(TAG)

Preston
